        <Parent_String>capital components [300001698], capitals and capital components [300065036], column components [300001650], columns and column components [300052248], supporting and resisting elements [300078047], structural elements [300078048], structural elements and components for structural elements [300078046], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
